Interface Sendable

All Known Implementing Classes:
ChatMessage, CreateMessage, DisconnectMessage, EndGameMessage, JoinMessage, LastRoundMessage, LeaveMessage, ListMessage, LocalBoard, LocalBookshelf, LocalCommonCard, LocalGame, LocalHand, LocalPersonalCard, LocalPlayer, LocalPlayerList, NewTurnMessage, OrderMessage, PickMessage, PingMessage, PutMessage, ReconnectMessage, StartGameMessage, TimerMessage, UndoMessage
public interface Sendable
The Sendable interface represents a message that can be sent between client and server. It provides a method to retrieve the message header.
